and it doesn't seem like that attitude is as much found in places like data science,

00:38:49.520 --> 00:38:54.159
and so I guess I'm just kind of interested in your perspective on the relationship between

00:38:54.159 --> 00:39:00.000
those different fields and how they interact outside with, you know, other fields.

